name: Maddy Cheary
description:
My first attempt so please don't judge too harshly. Although any tips for improvement I would really appreciate.

I can’t say much about Maddy Cheary, just another bimbo model from Instagram, but I really like her facial features.

Version 2: Completely retrained model from scratch

I recommend reduced weight. For example, "(madd1chear2:0.9)" works fine in most cases

Also, for maximum similarity to the original, I recommend adding "busty" before the trigger word and "freckles" in your prompts.
